# Bookcovers

This is a completely experiemental project to generate SVG and PNG book covers
using HTML5 canvas.

## Getting started

To get set up:

```
git clone git@github.com:thoughtbot/book-covers.git
cd book-covers
bundle install
```

## Develop

Run the server:

```
middleman
```

Open a browser:

```
open http://localhost:4567
```

